IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE 15TH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT IN AND FOR PALM BEACH COUNTY FLORIDA

JANE DOE, by and through JANE DOE'S MOTHER, as parent and natural guardian
Plaintiff

vs.

JEFFREY EPSTEIN, HALEY ROBSON and SARAH KELLEN
Defendant

Case No: 50 2008 CA 006596 XXXX MB AB
Florida Bar No: 089737

NOTICE OF CANCELLATION OF HEARINGS

YOU ARE HEREBY NOTIFIED that the following hearings scheduled for June 18, 2008 on Defendant Epstein's Motion for Enlargement of Time and Defendant Robson's Motion to Quash Service of Process have been CANCELLED.

I hereby certify that a good faith effort has been made to resolve the issues herein, or same shall be made prior to the hearing.

I HEREBY CERTIFY that a true and correct copy of the foregoing was served by U.S.Mail this 18 day of June, 2008, to all counsel on the attached service list.
